2026-05-10T17:45:33.5953257Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5953932Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5954959Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5955786Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5956607Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5957652Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5958492Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5959301Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5960052Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-10T17:45:33.5960633Z 33    -->
